dialogue.text: Sensei...
Wake up...
...Ayane?
I take it we both fell asleep?
Is there a {i}reason{/i} for this silence? Or...
Sensei...
...What?
I think...
I think something happened...
What do you mean “something happened?” Did that weird picture-wall go down?
Um...
Yeah, but...
I think you should...probably go see for yourself...
The sky is back to normal.
Yeah, but...
Everything {i}else{/i} isn’t.
All the stuff I brought up here is...well, it's still {i}here.{/i} And I didn’t see anyone when I went downstairs to use the restroom.
No one’s answering their phone either. And I’ve tried everyone.
This...hasn’t ever happened before, has it? Where...the world resets but...no one {i}else{/i} goes with it?
No...it hasn’t.
Well...what should we do?
Do you want to, like...look around or something? Maybe today is just a holiday and...and all the girls are grouped up somewhere else?
Or...or maybe it would be safer to stay put? Maybe the reset’s only, like...halfway done? Maybe we just need to wait out the rest?
What if this isn’t a reset?
What else would it be?
I have no idea.
Maybe it’s a whole new world entirely. Maybe we really {i}did{/i} live through the apocalypse. I don’t fucking know. It doesn’t make sense.
Well...well if...that wall is gone...we can go out and look for Maya, right? Even if it’s a risk. Maybe she’ll know what’s going on?
Or maybe she’s gone and we’re the only people left? Maybe we’ve got a whole fucking world to ourselves now and everything else is fucked?
Or maybe not? Maybe there’s still a chance to...you know...fix things?
It’s good to see you managed to find your optimism again. It just kind of sucks that it took a botched reset in order to bring it back. It would have been really helpful last night.
...I’m sorry. I didn’t mean that.
I know...I’m not upset. I’d probably be lashing out even more if I was in your shoes.
You {i}are{/i} in my shoes. It’s not like I’m the only person impacted by everyone and everything suddenly vanishing.
No...but I know how badly you wanted to see Maya again. And all I did last night was-
Maya’s still here. We just have to find her. And once we do, the world will fix itself.
Sensei...
She’s clearly necessary for the reset to work properly if {i}this{/i} is what we get when she’s not here.
Which one is it? Is everyone and everything gone? Or are we going to try and keep hope alive by saying Maya is somehow exempt from all of that?
I’ll give you an answer when I think of one. For now, we need to get off of this roof and...do {i}something.{/i} Anything.
...Okay.
But if we can’t find anyone...and it really is just us left...what then?
Do {i}you{/i} have an answer to that question? Because I sure as hell don’t.
Then...I guess that’s just a bridge we’ll have to cross if we ever get to it.
I really hope we don’t, Ayane...
I really hope we don’t.
This is kind of creepy, isn’t it?

It’s one thing to wander the halls of the school while the sky is eating itself and the moon is growing larger by the second, but there’s something even {i}more{/i} unsettling about being alone here in the light.
I think you’re just used to the former already. And you’ll have plenty of time to get used to this as well if we really are alone.
On the bright side, at least we’ll be able to have sex in all of the classrooms without getting in trouble.
I don’t want to talk about sex right now, Ayane.
That’s how you know it’s bad.
Indeed. It is {i}very{/i} bad.
But I doubt it’s going to get any better if we just stare outside the window waiting for something to happen.
It...feels kind of weird leaving after being stuck here for over a month. Surreal, even.
More surreal than a sky made up of pictures and making coffee on an old school desk?
When that’s what you’ve gotten used to, yeah. Going back to normal {i}is{/i} surreal after spending so much time in a world that doesn’t even seem possible.
This is anything but normal and you know that.
I’m not sure I {i}know{/i} anything anymore. It’s like any time I manage to pull myself out of {i}one{/i} crisis, another takes its place.
Maybe Maya’s been wrong this whole time and {i}I’m{/i} the most unlucky girl to ever exist?
You can tell her that when you see her later and I’m sure she’ll have some sort of witty counterpoint to make you eat your words.
I hope so...
I just keep thinking about the last thing I said to her.
What was it?
Something mean. But it made sense in the moment.
Do you remember the last thing {i}you{/i} said to her?
No.
I don’t.
So, what’ll be the first stop on Sensei & Ayane’s post-apocalyptic field-trip through Kumon-mi {i}this{/i} time?
The dorms. That’s where we found her the last time she vanished, and I’m willing to bet it’s where we’ll find her again this time.
Would you mind if we stopped at a few other places first?
Like?
Anywhere people might gather. The park....Koi Cafe...things like that. Nothing too far.
Is that really necessary?
It wouldn’t hurt, I don’t think. And if there {i}is{/i} anyone left, I imagine they’d group up somewhere, like...public. Somewhere that everyone visits regularly.
You mean...like the school?
For all we know, they might not have been able to {i}get{/i} to the school. That wall could have boxed the two of us in while everyone else wondered where {i}we{/i} went.
That seems...highly improbable.
Literally everything about this is highly improbable. But if you really don’t think it’s a good idea, we can-
It’s fine...
Like you said, it won’t hurt.
And finding {i}anyone{/i} would, at the bare minimum, help us get a better idea of what might be going on here. Especially if they’ve been...{i}conscious{/i} anywhere near as long as you have.
Thank you for not abusing your power as someone who may very well be the last man on earth while the last {i}girl{/i} on earth is much smaller and weaker than you.
Smaller, yes. Weaker? Doubtful. You know karate.
I’ll teach you everything I know if we’re unable to find anyone. And you’ll have plenty of time to learn since you don’t want to impregnate me and repopulate the world.
Let’s just...focus on finding someone first, Ayane. {i}Then{/i} we can talk about repopulating.
There is no one at the park.
There is no one on the street we take to school.
And there is no one at Koi Cafe.
Okay. I’m willing to admit my idea was a bust now.
I had a feeling it would be.
Thank you for humoring me regardless. I just...
I really had a feeling like we’d find someone here. And after you managed to track down Maya the first time, I wanted to be of some use {i}this{/i} time and-
It’s fine. Let’s just get to the dorms. We’ve used up enough time getting partially sidetracked like this.
Are you {i}really{/i} sure that’s where you want to go next, Sensei?
Yeah, that’s why I mentioned it in the very beginning of our “field trip.” Why does it sound like you’re about to try and talk me out of it?
That’s...
Um...
Well...you remember last night...when we were talking about, like...voices and stuff?
It’s faint, and...I’m not really sure if I’d even call it a {i}voice,{/i} but...
It’s like something in the back of mind is telling me we shouldn’t go there yet.
Weren’t you {i}just{/i} telling me last night that those “voices” don’t need to be taken as gospel? We’re not obligated to listen to them. And I’m not willing to risk waiting around any longer.
Yeah.
I understand...
Great. Then, let’s get going.
W-Wait! Sensei!
What now, Ayane?
Oh, I just want to get this rock out of my boot before...got it. Okay, we’re good.
Did I really need to be stopped for that?
There is no one outside of the dorms.
But that’s okay.
There was no one outside of them the other time she vanished either and we still managed to find her.
{i}I{/i} managed to find her.
And I’ll find her again, no matter how many places I need to search.
Sensei...
Don’t try and talk me out of going inside, Ayane.
I won’t...and I’ll be right there with you.
I just...I don’t want to see you lose hope if she isn’t there. And I feel like you will.
I won’t.
But I feel like you will.
I told you, I won’t.
But I feel like you-
There is no one in the dorms.
There’s no one in the dorms.
There’s no one here.
She’s not here.
She’s not here because I killed her in Paper City.
See? I knew this was going to happen.
We really are alone...aren’t we?
Yes, but there are still places we can look.
She’s not here...
There’s no one in the dorms.
There’s no one anywhere.
Sensei, look at me.
I look at her.
You need to calm down.
I am calm. I’m calm as can be. I’m the calmest I’ve ever been. I’m calm. I’m so calm. I’m calm, Ayane. I am.
No, you’re not. And I get that you’ve been doing your best to keep it together ever since you woke up, but you need to do {i}better.{/i}
You need to {i}fight.{/i}
Fight? Fight what? What the fuck do you want me to do? Am I not allowed to freak out for a second while I come to terms with the fact that I might never see Maya again?
No.
You’re not, actually.
You’re not allowed to freak out at all.
You have to stay completely calm and {i}fight{/i} because, if you don’t, you won’t ever get out of this.
What the fuck do you mean?! How do you know that?!
I know it because you haven’t even made it out of the house yet.
What?!
What?
You shouldn’t have opened the door.
Hah...hah...hah!
Fuck! Right there! Right there, baby!
Ohhh my god! I’m gonna cum...you’re gonna make me cum!
You like my pussy, baby?...You like...fucking me like that?...Yeah?...
Sana?...
Guess again......asshole......
Hah....hah....hah....
Blackout sex......really {i}is{/i} the best......
Maya?...
Well, well, well...
Look who.....finally decided to show up...
This...
We can’t-
Don’t you dare...fucking stop...
But you-
I repeat......{i}don’t you dare fucking stop...{/i}
{i}God{/i} that feels so good. Holy shit.
Harder......
{i}Faster......{/i}
But...but...won’t I...
You’ll be fine...
{i}Me{/i} on the other hand?...
I am {i}fucked...{/i}Both literally and figuratively...
What does that mean?! What’s going to happen to you?!
Probably the...same thing that happened to you all those...times I couldn’t hold myself back...
First...I’m going to cum {i}so fucking hard...{/i}
Then...
I’ll be reset...
{i}Then{/i} what?!
That’s it...there’s no third step after that...
That’s {i}worse{/i} than me being reset! How am I supposed to do any of this without you?!
You’ll figure it out...You’re smart...
No I'm not! Not even close!
Then...you're creative?...
I’ll get your memories back...I swear. I’ll do it.
Good fucking luck. It took me a zillion years to get any of {i}yours{/i} back and we probably won’t even get to cuddle after this...
How do you know?! How do you know it’ll be you instead of me?!
Because...idiot...
It’s already started...
If it weren’t for the...costume you tore off of me...I wouldn’t even know what day it is right now...
That doesn’t mean anything. That-
Give it a...fucking break, would you?...Just screw me and...let my mind get wiped on a slightly happier note...
Her legs wrap around my waist and push me in deeper, but despite my mind’s desperate pleas to put an end to this, my body refuses to let up.
I press her hands harder into the concrete of the same rooftop where she changed my life and force my eyes shut so I can pretend this isn’t happening.
Open your eyes...pervert...you know you...can’t resist me...
They don’t stay closed for long, though.
Maya...
That's me...
I love you...
I know...
God I...almost forgot...how big you are...that’s so good...that’s so fucking good...
Why do you get to close your eyes but not me?...
I was just...blinking...
If you want to play that game...I won’t take my eyes off of you again until this is all over...
Then I’ll make it last forever...
That’s even...more impossible than the...memory thing...
I bet you...want to cum right now...don’t you?...
I’d ask if you’ve been...saving up for me, but...we both know you’ve been {i}spreading your love{/i} all over the place...this whole fucking time...
Are you jealous?...
{i}Very.{/i} Angry too. You’re supposed to be {i}my{/i} man. And I’ve been so loyal this whole time.
Except for all those other me’s you apparently seduced.
They didn’t count.
Mngh.....mmf.....hmngh.....
I’m surprised you’re...still hanging in there...
The same goes for you...I imagined you would have crumbled by now based on how long you’ve wanted this...
I got a head start...remember?...Sucks you had to miss my first few orgasms...I came as soon as you put it in...
You must really like me...
Or I’m just very easy to please...
Mmf.......mmngh.......mm!
You want to cum again, don’t you?...
Yeah...
But...
I don’t want to disappear...
I want to stay here...with you...
I’ll get you back...
Do you promise?...
I promise...
You better mean that! I’ll never forgive you if you don’t!
Ngh!!!
Are you okay? Was that too hard?
It’s...perfect! But...I’m...ngh!
Hngh...ngh....ngh!
How much time do you have left?...
Not much...
I’ve already...given up everything else...
All that’s left.....are the memories of you!...
The ones I...treasure most of all!
The memories of...my Akira!
Say it again...
Akira!
Again...
Akira, Akira, Akira!
Again!
Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira, Akira!!!!!!
I love you more than anything!
